{{ heading('Typescale', '3') }}

{{ heading('Heading', '4') }}
<p>Headings come in a range of sizes for different contexts:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>2xl</strong> and <strong>xl</strong> are suitable for dashboard metrics, hero / high emphasis content.</li>
  <li><strong>xl</strong> and <strong>lg</strong> are suitable for page titles.</li>
  <li><strong>md</strong> can be used in large components where space is not limited and perfectly balances with Body M, such as modals.</li>
  <li><strong>sm</strong> and <strong>xs</strong> are for titles in small components where space is limited, such as flags.</li>
  <li><strong>xs</strong> is suitable for lower level titles and when matched with Body sm, for example, in fine print.</li>
</ul>
{{ typescaleTable(tokens.text.heading) }}

